title: Spiked
description:
Chris shows up late forcing the podcast to start 30 minutes behind schedule (00:00:10). Florida Governor Ron DeSantis wants this mask theater to end (00:11:00). Alex Reimer's deletes his Tony Massarotti scoop tweet from Twitter (00:15:41). Chris presses Kirk on his break announcement (00:41:00). One of Chris' most confusing activities, Tiger Woods trolls Phil Mickelson & much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
